                  <div id="mainContent">
                     <h2>Student Spaces</h2>
                     			
                     <p class="intro">The College of Engineering and Computing offers a variety of spaces for students to
                        utilize.</p>
                     
                     		
                     <section class="content-body">
                        <div class="row row">
                           <div class="column grid_9">
                              			
                              <h3>Explore the different spaces within the CEC by clicking on an image to see more.</h3>
                              
                              <ul class="grid img-list">
                                 <li><a class="fancybox" title="The Swearingen Center is located at 301 Main St. Columbia, SC 29208." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/4975f3a1-fc16-4d3e-a492-38d67ffe9b2d.jpg" rel="group282941">
                                       <div class="li-img"><img src="/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/images/connect/swearingen_center.jpg" alt="Outside of Swearingen Engineering Center" width="255" height="255"></div>
                                       <div class="li-text">
                                          <h3 class="li-head">Swearingen Center</h3>
                                          <p class="li-sub">
                                             The Swearingen Center has been the home of the College of Engineering and Computing
                                             since 1987. The Swearingen Center houses Chemical and Electrical Engineering departments.
                                             </p>
                                       </div></a><div style="display:none"><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Picnic tables in the courtyard are available for students to socialize and study." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/1c2905be-d794-43b8-bda6-1bcb89a36f4e.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="There are multiple computer labs with software downloaded for students to utilize for classwork and are available 24/7." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/fd49a556-55e2-492c-9a08-dbe45b97fbec.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Grab a coffee or a sandwich in the Wired Café." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/fc512e3d-d570-448c-b2ca-341663f5a99e.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Students enjoy a meal at the Wired Café while studying." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/57a2c0ed-6ec7-49b9-81b3-b4707fd62300.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="TVs are available in the Wired Cafe to collaborate with HDMI ports." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/a27a2271-04e6-434a-84c5-26874b3599b2.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The first floor lobby entrance to the Swearingen Center looks out to the Courtyard." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/7a919965-3126-448e-b2c2-0c40cfefce7f.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Undergraduate students can talk to advisors and access resources in Student Services, located on the first floor." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/12701854-9c0e-43fc-8936-2e5c730b60b6.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Amoco Hall is a lecture hall that holds about 300 people." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/c4455623-2b27-482f-92ce-70b1bc1192d5.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Dean's office is located on the third floor of the Swearingen Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/fd26ba33-c5c8-4168-b3a7-481d0c38a6f6.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Chemical Engineering Offices are located on the second floor of the Swearingen Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/83f075fd-d459-42f1-a775-dfd93e8375c7.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Electrical Engineering Offices are located on the third floor of the Swearingen Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/4b835caa-e126-40ab-8524-f65a276edcad.jpg" rel="group282941"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Student can work with peer mentors for tutoring services. " href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282941/production/master/febd2b38-a500-4f9a-a611-e62965684a83.jpg" rel="group282941"></a></div>
                                 </li>
                                 <li><a class="fancybox" title="The 300 Main building is located at 300 Main St.&#xA;Columbia, SC 29208." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/96c70bcd-b87a-40d7-abaa-1e08f083be4e.jpg" rel="group284557">
                                       <div class="li-img"><img src="/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/images/students/300_main_callout.jpg" alt="Outside of 300 Main" width="255" height="255"></div>
                                       <div class="li-text">
                                          <h3 class="li-head">300 Main</h3>
                                          <p class="li-sub">
                                             The 300 Main Building is home to the Civil and Environmental Engineering and Mechanical
                                             Engineering Departments as well as student lab space and classrooms.
                                             </p>
                                       </div></a><div style="display:none"><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Lobby entrance to 300 Main. " href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/4d59eea1-3588-4b3b-a1d8-d51930ae9f98.jpg" rel="group284557"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Civil and Environmental Engineering department can be found on the second floor of 300 Main." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/51ce4d16-e560-49cd-9784-52d905068a6a.jpg" rel="group284557"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Mechanical Engineering department can be found on the second floor of 300 Main." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/c406364c-4fd2-48f6-a7a5-472ff71f5621.jpg" rel="group284557"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Structures Lab has large machinery, steel pillars and railroad tracks for student and faculty research." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/2870de40-9f29-443e-a3ee-3cbc43d8cb87.jpg" rel="group284557"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Water Lab is a large container with water and a variety of pumps to observe water flow." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/351f0690-15db-41bf-9410-cc45dba5e667.jpg" rel="group284557"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Lab space with equipment for students to use. " href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/fc719b96-b7e7-4c3a-8ee3-256aa2240589.jpg" rel="group284557"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="A classroom in the 300 Main building." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/1ddbc219-8a6e-490a-bb1e-46d520b0f04e.jpg" rel="group284557"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Students can get an interactive learning experience in the Mechanical Engineering lab. " href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/5a4b6e17-0089-442b-a726-c7fe3ee5d0ce.jpg" rel="group284557"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Students have access to tools and work space to learn in different space." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284557/production/master/65952579-aaab-4da8-80f3-b7d8152888a4.jpg" rel="group284557"></a></div>
                                 </li>
                                 <li><a class="fancybox" title="M. Bert Storey Engineering and Innovation Center is located at 550 Assembly St. Columbia, SC 29201." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/e7785414-9e10-4fa9-b989-91be2766ce40.jpg" rel="group284546">
                                       <div class="li-img"><img src="/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/images/connect/m_bert_storey_center.jpg" alt="Outside of M. Bert Storey Engineering and Innovation Center" width="255" height="255"></div>
                                       <div class="li-text">
                                          <h3 class="li-head">M. Bert Storey Engineering and Innovation Center</h3>
                                          <p class="li-sub">
                                             The M. Bert Storey Engineering and Innovation Center houses Computer Science and Engineering
                                             and Integrated Information Technology departments.
                                             </p>
                                       </div></a><div style="display:none"><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Computer Science and Engineering department is located on the second floor in the M. Bert Storey Engineering and Innovation Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/98a18c00-914c-420d-a084-0f64440477a5.jpg" rel="group284546"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Integrated Information Technology Department is located on the first floor in the M. Bert Storey Engineering and Innovation Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/2338571c-9cd8-4f0f-81cc-a2738da6b17b.jpg" rel="group284546"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Three maps that display where CEC students with internships are located." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/5d65e4d3-42ae-458d-929c-58ac0940c9db.jpg" rel="group284546"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The lobby entrance to the M. Bert Storey Engineering and Innovation Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/f82da5dc-414d-4c77-9826-3a7893101d89.jpg" rel="group284546"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="A large classroom with desks and chairs for students." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/47095879-9eda-44cc-8554-7b476a02b646.jpg" rel="group284546"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="A seminar room with desks and chairs for students." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/a8a8e558-09e6-4ee0-8044-a50f334b26c5.jpg" rel="group284546"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Cubical desks spaces and computers for graduate students." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/60768831-49db-4218-bca6-5a08396dccfe.jpg" rel="group284546"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Computer labs are available for students to use." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/f7b25bec-03b8-4537-b36a-51b2d23ffde3.jpg" rel="group284546"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Computer lab classrooms are available for students and used to complete class work." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a284546/production/master/460db141-3943-4990-8b03-b2f39808f76d.jpg" rel="group284546"></a></div>
                                 </li>
                                 <li><a class="fancybox" title="The McNair Aerospace Center building is located 1000 Catawba St Suite 120, Columbia, SC 29201." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283069/production/master/fabf9223-c7c3-4842-bdfd-9c3bd1c2f591.jpg" rel="group283069">
                                       <div class="li-img"><img src="/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/images/students/mcnair_outside_grid.jpg" alt="outside of the mcnair center" width="255" height="255"></div>
                                       <div class="li-text">
                                          <h3 class="li-head">McNair Aerospace Center</h3>
                                          <p class="li-sub">
                                             The McNair Aerospace Center's mission is to support this rapidly growing industry
                                             by offering aerospace education, research, outreach and economic engagement.
                                             </p>
                                       </div></a><div style="display:none"><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="A full sized Apache Helicopter on display in the McNair Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283069/production/master/570acd60-3cc8-491d-bab3-e99259e167fa.jpg" rel="group283069"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Students use the flight simulators for their aerospace education." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283069/production/master/989b3118-3a2e-4ade-81fe-16e66ddebea4.jpg" rel="group283069"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The neXt Future Factories Lab is used for research done in the McNair Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283069/production/master/e0beb4cd-8d41-4d25-976d-021fa592508a.jpg" rel="group283069"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The McNair Center has research stations that include computers and desks." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283069/production/master/4c69c145-1507-4e4b-b689-85d15a75c42f.jpg" rel="group283069"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="A high temperature curing oven is used for research." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283069/production/master/cc8cbf93-28e4-48a8-9f95-a0db60439216.jpg" rel="group283069"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Lynx Automated Fiber Placement Machine." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283069/production/master/9e1769ff-0b4e-4112-bce6-f1333db08864.jpg" rel="group283069"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Digital Transformation Lab showcases eight different areas including Digital Transformation, MSG Like for Army Aviation, Advancing Wire Harness Manufacturing, Predictive Manufacturing Solutions, Capstone Design Program, Factory for the Future, Advancing Automated Fiber Placement, NASA and University Leadership Initiatives." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283069/production/master/e94afede-3218-45da-91d1-13df95187045.jpg" rel="group283069"></a></div>
                                 </li>
                                 <li><a class="fancybox" title="Two students working in the Rapid Prototyping Lab located in Room 1D25 in the Swearingen Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283012/production/master/62f1f845-37bc-488b-b323-b635d446a5c6.JPG" rel="group283012">
                                       <div class="li-img"><img src="/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/images/students/makersspace_callout.jpg" alt="Placeholder Grid Image" width="255" height="255"></div>
                                       <div class="li-text">
                                          <h3 class="li-head">Makerspaces</h3>
                                          <p class="li-sub">
                                             The Makerspaces are made up of The Rapid Prototyping Lab and The Student Access Machine Shop. The spaces offer unique
                                             tools, including 3D printing, for students to use.
                                             </p>
                                       </div></a><div style="display:none"><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="A student 3D printing." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283012/production/master/d84facf7-6b5c-4165-9f5e-bf2645fca821.JPG" rel="group283012"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="Shelves with 3D printers and completed projects on display." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a283012/production/master/1917b119-d1d7-482b-a051-4fddf4f69e29.JPG" rel="group283012"></a></div>
                                 </li>
                                 <li><a class="fancybox" title="Students can learn more about career fairs, career preparation and many other resources at Career Center on the first floor of the Swearingen Center." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282986/production/master/05e95709-97c5-47ff-9858-cda6dc4e7999.jpg" rel="group282986">
                                       <div class="li-img"><img src="/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/images/students/career-center/career_center_office_callout.jpg" alt="sign that says 'I am a fan of the career center'" width="255" height="255"></div>
                                       <div class="li-text">
                                          <h3 class="li-head">Career Center</h3>
                                          <p class="li-sub">The CEC Career Center satellite office offers career related resources and helps students
                                             find internships, co-ops or jobs,</p>
                                       </div></a><div style="display:none"><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Career Center helps students prepare for interviews, find jobs and offers a variety of professional resources." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282986/production/master/4556c082-c0ee-44d3-b582-bd2a2203f39d.jpg" rel="group282986"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Career Center has many resources including  practice mock interviews which are held in these offices." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282986/production/master/2bd0019f-dd3e-4312-91a5-be889b0b47fd.jpg" rel="group282986"></a><a style="display:none" class="fancybox" title="The Career Center hosts many events, including Advice with a Slice which prepares students for the annual STEM Career Fair." href="https://www.sc.edu/study/colleges_schools/engineering_and_computing/_resources/ldp-galleries/.private_ldp/a282986/production/master/4ece1a2c-9386-4de4-a067-51e57a4e943c.jpg" rel="group282986"></a></div>
                                 </li>
                              </ul>
                              
                              <p>&nbsp;</p>
                              
                              		</div>
                        </div>
